org.jmlspecs.ant.tasks
Class FileSetWrapper

java.lang.Object
  org.jmlspecs.ant.tasks.FileSetWrapper
public class FileSetWrapper
extends Object

The inner class Visitor is provided to conveniently perform a certain action on all element in a FileSet. It is typically used as follows in a task:


 fileset.new Visitor() {
   public void visit(File file) {
     //action code
   }
 }.visit(project);
